      • createRoutingProblem

        public static com.graphhopper.jsprit.core.problem.VehicleRoutingProblem createRoutingProblem(Carrier carrier,
                                                                                             Network network,
                                                                                             com.graphhopper.jsprit.core.problem.cost.VehicleRoutingTransportCosts transportCosts,
                                                                                             com.graphhopper.jsprit.core.problem.cost.VehicleRoutingActivityCosts activityCosts)
        Creates an immutable VehicleRoutingProblem from Carrier.

        For creation it takes only the information needed to setup the problem (not the solution, i.e. predefined plans are ignored).

        The network is required to retrieve coordinates of locations.

        Note that currently only services (Service) are supported.

        Throws:
        IllegalStateException - if shipments are involved.

      • createRoutingProblemBuilder

        public static com.graphhopper.jsprit.core.problem.VehicleRoutingProblem.Builder createRoutingProblemBuilder(Carrier carrier,
                                                                                                            Network network)
        Creates VehicleRoutingProblem.Builder from Carrier for later building of the VehicleRoutingProblem. This is required if you need to add stuff to the problem later, e.g. because it cannot solely be retrieved from network and carrier such as NetworkBasedTransportCosts.

        For creation it takes only the information needed to setup the problem (not the solution, i.e. predefined plans are ignored).

        The network is required to retrieve coordinates of locations.

        Note that currently only services (Service) are supported.

        Throws:
        IllegalStateException - if shipments are involved.

      • createCarrier

        public static Carrier createCarrier(String carrierId,
                                    com.graphhopper.jsprit.core.problem.VehicleRoutingProblem vrp)
        Creates a Carrier from VehicleRoutingProblem. The carrier is initialized with the carrierId, i.e. carrier.getId() returns carrierId.

      • createPlan

        public static CarrierPlan createPlan(Carrier carrier,
                                     com.graphhopper.jsprit.core.problem.solution.VehicleRoutingProblemSolution solution)
        Creates a CarrierPlan from VehicleRoutingProblemSolution.

        Note that the costs of the solution are multiplied by -1 to represent the corresponding score of a carrierPlan.

        The input parameter Carrier is just required to initialize the plan.
